title: Financial Reporting
copy: Thanks to the generosity of our members, donors, volunteers, and friends, every year we are able to grow our global collection, expand our audience engagement, strengthen our exhibition program, and innovate our public programs for all ages. Our annual reports offer a snapshot of each year from July 1 of one year through June 30 of the following, coinciding with the museum’s fiscal calendar.   Please see our most recent reports below or our archive for all reports .
